messages.content: =Summarize this email using as few words as possible: {{ $('Gmail Trigger').first().json.text }}

Label: recgql6T2d2qIKncr
json.Initial Message:
Hey Markeisha, we currently have these homes available for rent (Section 8 welcome): 
 https://bit.ly/3126-126-Th-St 
 https://bit.ly/1113-Radcliffe-Dr 
 https://bit.ly/2202-Walnut-St 
 
 If you’re interested, then please fill out this brief questionnaire. It’s free and takes less than two minutes:
 https://bit.ly/imposbl 

Thank you!
json.SMS Tour:
Hey Markeisha, thanks for submitting your questionnaire! We currently have these homes available for rent (Section 8 welcome): 
 https://bit.ly/3126-126-Th-St 
 https://bit.ly/1113-Radcliffe-Dr 
 https://bit.ly/2202-Walnut-St 
 
 Please let me know which you are interested in, I will be happy to set up a tour. Thanks!
json.Followup Message: Hey Markeisha, are you still looking for an affordable home?
